er":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563771612","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546275050,"updated_time":1546275211,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":10,"content":"\u003cp\u003e知乎最大民科成了，让我简单概括下这哥们的思路。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e首先他假设-1是质数然后用逆否命题证明-1加任意质数是一个偶数的哥猜变式正确，然后再假设-1加任意数，即该任意数不为质数，把-1的式子去掉，然后轻松得到6k是哥猜范围里且正确的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e接下来他继续用这个方法证明了6k-2和6k+2是在哥猜范围且正确的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然后这三个组合代表了所有在哥猜范围里的偶数，即哥猜正确。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e对此，我只想说，你这么牛逼咋不直接写无法证伪哥猜，所以哥猜正确呢。。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563789729,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b53af4e6943aa6c0e3651512f5c13b89","url_token":"yang-yi-66-95","name":"杨溢","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/8e6a1213f_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/8e6a1213f_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/b53af4e6943aa6c0e3651512f5c13b89","user_type":"people","headline":"FGA，有专利，攻读地质学，曾涉猎生物学、化学，业余于经济学。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563789729","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546277409,"updated_time":1546277409,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e只吃练实的凤凰会在意猫头鹰的老鼠嘛？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562320036,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"c995941e69c85ca4